@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "My Project Brief";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<section>
    <h2>Company Info</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Company/Business Name</th>
            <td>XYZ Solutions</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Company Description</th>
            <td>Our company, XYZ Solutions, is a dynamic and innovative tech startup specializing in web development and e-commerce solutions.
                 Established in 2021, we are dedicated to providing cutting-edge technology services to our clients, helping them succeed in the 
                 digital age. With a team of passionate and skilled professionals, we have successfully delivered a wide range of web-based 
                 projects, from small business websites to complex e-commerce platforms. Our mission is to empower businesses by harnessing the
                  power of the internet and technology. At XYZ Solutions, we pride ourselves on our commitment to excellence, creativity, and client
                   satisfaction. We believe in building long-lasting relationships with our clients, understanding their unique needs, and delivering
                    tailor-made solutions that drive results. As a forward-thinking company, we stay updated with the latest industry trends and 
                    technologies, ensuring that our clients benefit from the most advanced and efficient solutions. We look forward to the 
                    opportunity to work with you and contribute to the success of your project.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Group Members and Roles</th>
            <td>
                <ul>
                    <li>Front-end Developer</li>
                    <li>Back-end Developer</li>
                    <li>Full Stack</li>
                </ul>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Proposal</h2>
    <p>
        Our website, XYZ Solutions, is designed to be a versatile online platform that serves as a one-stop solution for [briefly describe 
        the main purpose or focus of my website]. It aims to provide a seamless and engaging user experience for visitors, catering to a wide 
        range of needs and preferences.
   </p>
    <p>
         At XYZ Solutions, we are committed to delivering a feature-rich website that offers [mention key features or functionalities of 
         my site]. Whether users are seeking information, products, services, or community engagement, our platform will be the go-to destination.
    </p>
    <p>
        Our site will primarily target [describe my target audience, such as demographics, interests, or industries]. By understanding their
         unique needs and preferences, we will ensure that our website delivers value and meets their expectations.
    </p>
    <p>
        The core roles and functionalities of our website include:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Admin: The admin role is responsible for managing and maintaining the website. Admins have the following responsibilities: </li>
        
            <li>Content Management: Admins can create, edit, and delete content such as articles, products, and user accounts.</li>
            <li>User Management: They have the authority to add, modify, or remove user accounts, including granting special privileges.</li>
            <li>Site Configuration: Admins can configure site settings, including themes, permissions, and security settings.</li>
            <li>Moderation: Admins may oversee user-generated content and ensure that it complies with community guidelines.</li>
            
        
        <li>Customers: Customers are the primary users of our website. They can interact with the site in the following ways:</li>
           
            <li>Browsing: Customers can browse the website, view products or content, and access information without the need for an account.</li>
            <li>Registration: Customers have the option to register for an account, which allows them to access additional features, such as:
                
                    <li>Ordering Products: Registered customers can place orders for products or services through our e-commerce platform.</li>
                    <li>Personalized Experience: They can customize their profiles, save preferences, and receive tailored recommendations.</li>
                    <li>Communication: Registered customers may subscribe to newsletters, receive updates, and interact with the community.</li>
                    
        <li>Members: Members are a subset of registered users who gain additional benefits or privileges. These benefits may include:</li>

             <li>Exclusive Content: Members have access to exclusive content, services, or resources that are not available to standard customers.</li>
            <li>Discounts and Rewards: Members may be eligible for special discounts, rewards programs, or loyalty points.</li>
            <li>Community Participation: They can actively participate in forums, discussions, or community events.</li>
            
    </ul>
</section>



       
